492
00:37:51,820 --> 00:37:58,500
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, i u području transporta, postoji puno razloka

493
00:37:58,500 --> 00:38:05,119
[SPEAKER_03] zbog čega bi klijenti banaka mogli biti,

494
00:38:05,119 --> 00:38:11,340
[SPEAKER_03] evo, možda bi banke mogli biti nesklone da im daju kredite,

495
00:38:11,340 --> 00:38:14,179
[SPEAKER_03] upravo zbog njihove izloženosti klimatskim rizicima.

496
00:38:14,179 --> 00:38:19,420
[SPEAKER_06] Slušam, izvolite, mikrofon vas molim samo, samo sekundu,

497
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:20,199
[SPEAKER_06] budite ljubazni.

498
00:38:20,199 --> 00:38:23,260
[SPEAKER_06] Da pače, da pače.

499
00:38:23,260 --> 00:38:26,659
