529
00:40:32,460 --> 00:40:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kada vam kažem da u strategiji prilagodbe predviđaju urokove,

530
00:40:36,539 --> 00:40:42,639
[SPEAKER_00] znači do 2040. što će biti, sa pogledom na 2070.

531
00:40:42,639 --> 00:40:47,460
