532
00:40:47,460 --> 00:40:51,139
[SPEAKER_00] ko ćemo li mi biti živi do tog trenutka i što će se uopće

533
00:40:51,139 --> 00:40:53,699
[SPEAKER_00] do 2070. godine dogoditi.

534
00:40:53,699 --> 00:40:57,960
